WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.667
Welcome to SwingVantage — your personal performance system for golf, tennis, baseball, and softball.

2
00:00:05.667 --> 00:00:11.333
Whatever you play, the goal is the same: help you get measurably better, your way.

3
00:00:11.333 --> 00:00:17.000
The idea is simple.

4
00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:22.667
Analyze your swing, see the single most important thing to work on, practice it with a focused plan, and watch yourself improve over time.

5
00:00:22.667 --> 00:00:28.333
Every feature works for free, across all seven sports.

6
00:00:28.333 --> 00:00:34.000
You get clear, honest feedback — and when the data is limited, SwingVantage tells you, instead of guessing.

7
00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:39.667
Getting started takes about two minutes.

8
00:00:39.667 --> 00:00:45.333
Just pick the sport you're working on — no account and no credit card needed — and you'll get your first personalized result right away.

9
00:00:45.333 --> 00:00:50.1000
From there, your Today dashboard becomes home base.

10
00:00:50.1000 --> 00:00:56.667
It shows your main focus, your recent sessions, your scores, and the single best thing to do next.

11
00:00:56.667 --> 00:01:02.333
And as you log more sessions, SwingVantage tracks your progress, so you can see real, lasting improvement.

12
00:01:02.333 --> 00:01:08.000
Welcome aboard — let's get started.
